{{Year nav topic5|1969|Portuguese television}}
This is a list of [[Portuguese television]] related events from 1969.

==Events==
*24 February - [[Simone de Oliveira]] is selected to represent Portugal at the [[Eurovision Song Contest 1969|1969 Eurovision Song Contest]] with her song "[[Desfolhada portuguesa|Desfolhada]]". She is selected to be the sixth Portuguese Eurovision entry during Festival da Canção held at Teatro São Luiz in Lisbon.<ref>[http://casacomum.org/cc/visualizador?pasta=06597.135.23285#!15/] from casacomum.org, February 24, 1969.</ref>

