{{TennisEventInfo|1980|Monte Carlo Open| | date=31 March – 6 April | edition=74th | category=[[Grand Prix tennis circuit|Grand Prix circuit]] | prize_money=$175,000 | draw=32S/16D | surface=[[Clay court|Clay]] / outdoor | location=[[Monte Carlo]], [[Monaco]] | venue=[[Monte Carlo Country Club]] | champs={{flagicon|SWE}} [[Björn Borg]] <ref name="ms">{{cite web|title=1980 Monte Carlo Men's Singles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/scores/archive/monte-carlo/410/1980/draws?matchType=singles|website=www.atpworldtour.com|publisher=[[Association of Tennis Professionals]] (ATP)}}</ref> | champd={{flagicon|ITA}} [[Paolo Bertolucci]] / {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Adriano Panatta]] <ref name=md>{{cite web|title=ATP – 1980 Monte Carlo Men's Doubles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/Share/Event-Draws.aspx?Year=1980&EventId=410&Draw=md|publisher=ATP}}</ref> }}
The '''1980 Monte Carlo Open''' was a men's [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Clay court|outdoor clay courts]] at the [[Monte Carlo Country Club]] in [[Monte Carlo]], [[Monaco]] that was part of the [[1980 Volvo Grand Prix]] circuit. It was the 74th edition of the tournament and was held from 31 March through 6 April 1980. First-seeded [[Björn Borg]] won the singles title, his third after 1977 and 1979.
==Champions== ===Singles=== {{flagicon|SWE}} '''[[Björn Borg]]''' defeated {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Guillermo Vilas]] 6–1, 6–0, 6–2
===Doubles=== {{flagicon|ITA}} '''[[Paolo Bertolucci]]''' / {{flagicon|ITA}} '''[[Adriano Panatta]]''' defeated {{flagicon|USA}} [[Vitas Gerulaitis]] / {{flagicon|USA}} [[John McEnroe]] 6–2, 5–7, 6–4
