'''"Du är inte ensam"''' ({{lang-en|You are not alone}}) is a song by [[Sweden|Swedish]] singer [[Julia Kedhammar]].  It [[Sweden in the Junior Eurovision Song Contest 2014|represented Sweden]] at the [[Junior Eurovision Song Contest 2014]] in [[Marsa, Malta]], placing 13th in a field of 16 songs, scoring 28 points.<ref name="Sweden">{{cite web|title=Julia Kedhammar chosen for Sweden!|url=http://www.junioreurovision.tv/page/blog?id=julia_kedhammar_chosen_for_sweden|last=Fisher|first=Luke James|work=Junioreurovision.tv|accessdate=6 June 2014|date=6 June 2014}}</ref>

