{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2015}} {{Infobox Magazine |title = Exame Informática |image_file = Exame Informática cover.jpg |image_size = |image_caption = |editor = |editor_title = |previous_editor = |staff_writer = |frequency = Monthly |circulation = |category = [[Computer magazine]] |company = |publisher =Medipress |firstdate = June 1995 |country = [[Portugal]] |based = [[Lisbon]] |language = [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] |website = http://aeiou.exameinformatica.pt/ |issn = }}
'''''Exame Informática''''' is a [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] monthly [[computer magazine]] published in Portugal.
==History and profile== ''Exame Informática'' was first published in June 1995.<ref name=exame>{{cite web|title=Exame Informatica|url=http://www.publicitas.com/switzerland/media-solutions/factsheet/mediadata/exame-informatica-portugal/?PARAM1=AL4EL3#.VIa6yGSsXRA|work=Publicitas|accessdate=9 December 2014}}</ref> The magazine is published monthly by Medipress Publishing and is based in [[Lisbon]].<ref name=exame/>
It is an [[information technology]] magazine<ref name=exame/> and every month is accompanied by a [[CD]] or a [[DVD]] (as is purchased or signed).
In 2007 ''Exame Informática'' had a circulation of 34,000 copies.<ref>{{cite web |author=Anne Austin et. al. |title=Western Europe Market and Media Fact |url=http://conan.lib.muohio.edu/ebooks/Western_Europe_Market_MediaFact_2008/Western%20Europe%20Market%20&%20MediaFact%202008.pdf |work=ZenithOptimedia |accessdate=11 April 2015 |date=2008 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205131709/http://conan.lib.muohio.edu/ebooks/Western_Europe_Market_MediaFact_2008/Western%20Europe%20Market%20%26%20MediaFact%202008.pdf |archivedate=5 February 2015 |df=dmy }}</ref>
