The diocese covers an area of 10,855&nbsp;km², and is a [[suffragan diocese]] of the [[Archdiocese of Ho Chi Minh city]].
[[Sacred Heart]] Cathedral in Thủ Dầu Một City is the [[Cathedral]] of the [[diocese]].<ref>[http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/phuc0.htm GCatholic.org]</ref>
